song_lyrics: Sakhī nand-maharne āngaṇe re, gopī ānand mangaḷ gāy,
Chhabī jone snehī Shyāmnī re... ṭek
Maramāḷe akhāḍo mānḍīyo re, kāju āsopālavnī chhāy... Chhabī 1
Vhāle prīt karīne paherīyo re, rūḍo sonerī suravāḷ... Chhabī 2
Sakhī faratā lāge chhe fūṭaḍī re, zīṇī angarkhīnī chāḷ... Chhabī 3
Bahumūlī moḷīḍu bāndhīyu re, kāju zaḷake sonerī kor... Chhabī 4
Rūḍā laṭakā kare chhe hāthnā re, Brahmānandno vahālo chitta-chor... Chhabī 5
title: Sakhī nand-maharne āngaṇe re
